#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fill_diagonal.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fill\\_diagonal"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:1 of
msgid "Fill the main diagonal of the given tensor of any dimensionality."
msgstr "填充任意维度张量的主对角线。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:3 of
msgid ""
"For a tensor `a` with ``a.ndim >= 2``, the diagonal is the list of "
"locations with indices ``a[i, ..., i]`` all identical. This function "
"modifies the input tensor in-place, it does not return a value."
msgstr ""
"对于一个 ``a.ndim >= 2`` 的张量 `a`，对角线是索引为 ``a[i, ..., i]`` 的"
"位置列表。此函数会就地修改输入张量，不返回值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:7 of
msgid "Tensor whose diagonal is to be filled, it gets modified in-place."
msgstr "要填充其对角线的张量，它将被就地修改。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:9 of
msgid ""
"Value to be written on the diagonal, its type must be compatible with "
"that of the tensor a."
msgstr "要写入对角线的值，其类型必须与张量 a 的类型兼容。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:12 of
msgid ""
"For tall matrices in NumPy version up to 1.6.2, the diagonal \"wrapped\" "
"after N columns. You can have this behavior with this option. This "
"affects only tall matrices."
msgstr ""
"对于 NumPy 1.6.2 及更早版本中的高矩阵，对角线在 N 列后会“换行”。你可以"
"通过此选项获得这种行为。这仅影响高矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:17 of
msgid ":py:obj:`diag_indices`, :py:obj:`diag_indices_from`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:20 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:21 of
msgid ""
"This functionality can be obtained via `diag_indices`, but internally "
"this version uses a much faster implementation that never constructs the "
"indices and uses simple slicing."
msgstr ""
"此功能可以通过 `diag_indices` 实现，但内部版本使用了一种更快速的实现方式"
"，它从不构造索引，而是使用简单的切片。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:26 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:35 of
msgid "The same function can operate on a 4-D tensor:"
msgstr "同一函数可以作用于 4 维张量："

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:40 of
msgid "We only show a few blocks for clarity:"
msgstr "为了清晰起见，我们只显示几个块："

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:55 of
msgid "The wrap option affects only tall matrices:"
msgstr "wrap 选项仅影响高矩阵："

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:85 of
msgid ""
"The anti-diagonal can be filled by reversing the order of elements using "
"either `numpy.flipud` or `numpy.fliplr`."
msgstr "可以通过使用 `numpy.flipud` 或 `numpy.fliplr` 反转元素顺序来填充反对角线。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.fill_diagonal.fill_diagonal:100 of
msgid ""
"Note that the order in which the diagonal is filled varies depending on "
"the flip function."
msgstr "请注意，对角线填充的顺序取决于所使用的翻转函数。"

